<br>
I know MF, Affliction and Magister are in zones that I wont see for quite some time but to be honest I'm not fussed. I know they're wearing better gear but I'm not some fawning psycophant that worries about it. I don't even look forward past armour which my guild is currently obtaining. I do not know the stats of Shining Knights armour but I'll be thankful when I get some. I think many of us &quot;lower end players&quot; ( Level 54 paladin here ) feel the same way. What many are terming as Uber is not having better gear, but having better gear, rubbing it in, and pretending that somehow that makes anyone better then anyone else.<br>
